                     <interp inst="t18471122-11-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>, stealing 1 tame fowl, price 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. and 1 sheet, value 3 <hi rend="italic">s</hi>. the property of <persName id="t18471122-name-134" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18471122-name-134" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18471122-name-134" type="surname" value="HOLGATE"></interp>
