                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant, T</hi> 1.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 31st Jan.</hi>, 1842, <hi rend="italic">having been before convicted; confined six months</hi>)—the prisoner is the man—he has been tried here since then, and at Horsemonger-lane.</p>
